{"tid":1787124,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"低成本來講 「屍殺片場」 同 「人肉搜索」 係咪有史以來拍得最好？","createTime":"2019-12-17T16:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:03:55.000Z","uid":42246,"like":73,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"952a91f3b0ad9d8306f4384d34416aa91ea4af77","tid":1787124,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jEbeUiV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjEbeUiV.jpg&h=72a88b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCL3NDV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCL3NDV.jpg&h=b29f3dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先低成本來講 通常d野都好撚假 cg呀 道具呀<br />\n屍殺用左拍電影來包裝 完美利用左「好假」依一點<br />\n人肉用左低成本既視窗世界來包裝 低成本又真<br />\n<br />\n路線<br />\n<br />\n屍殺行搞笑 動作路線<br />\n人肉用懸疑路線 <br />\n各有各做到佢應該要做既野 重要低成品得來 叫好好效果<br />\n<br />\n賣點 <br />\n屍殺玩一鏡過 同 真實拍戲過程<br />\n中段用意想不到發展 令前段所有野即刻合理化<br />\n<br />\n人肉用盡所有我地身邊常用社交媒體 <br />\n全用cam角度去睇（當然已經有幾套用過）<br />\n但人肉係用得最自然同得最緊湊<br />\n成套野1d都唔假<br />\n<br />\n成本<br />\n屍殺用左 23萬港幣 票房1.9億港幣<br />\n人肉用左 100萬美金 票房7000多萬美金<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩套野都係2018年之作 低成本之王"},{"pid":"364d817b75aa1664351837b25ad2eb54e6ee615e","tid":1787124,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5432a5754fec44dce45bcbaa247979b178ad89a3","tid":1787124,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93348007d961eec0dd4a2ea0b3ffc98c967a963b","tid":1787124,"uid":207826,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"條女幾正"},{"pid":"e75688bcd29c6ae525cbe17402e94faf6c5dcceb","tid":1787124,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫推<img 